RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

96-1270. VFW Post 1238 v. Ohio Liquor Control Comm.

Huron App. No. H-95-065. Reported at 78 Ohio St.3d 1482, 678 N.E.2d 946. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s motion to withdraw motion for reconsideration. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to withdraw motion for'reconsideration be, and hereby is, granted.

Resnick, J., not participating.
